            button#filterToggle(style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-light);") ✕ Đóng
          .filter-group
            h3 Khoảng giá
            label(
              style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px;font-size:0.88rem;cursor:pointer;"
              )
              input(
                checked="" 
                name="price" 
                type="radio"
                )
              | Dưới 10 triệu
            label(
              style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px;font-size:0.88rem;cursor:pointer;"
              )
              input(
                name="price" 
                type="radio"
                )
              | 10 – 25 triệu
